{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/dbusobjectproxysignalname\/notify"]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectProxySignalName\/notify"},"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"externalID":"s:3GIO25DBusObjectProxySignalNameO6notifyyA2CmF","symbolKind":"case","roleHeading":"Case","title":"DBusObjectProxySignalName.notify","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"notify","kind":"identifier"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectProxySignalName"]]},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"notify","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"derived GObject class. If the implementor did not create the property with","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then any call to "},{"code":"g_object_set_property()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" results"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in "},{"code":"notify","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" being emitted, even if the new value is the same as the old."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"If they did pass [explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then this signal is emitted only","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"when they explicitly call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify()"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and common practice is to do that only when the value has actually changed."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This signal is typically used to obtain change notification for a"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"single property, by specifying the property name as a detail in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"g_signal_connect()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" call, like this:"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"(C Language Example):","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"C","code":["g_signal_connect (text_view->buffer, \"notify::paste-target-list\",","                  G_CALLBACK (gtk_text_view_target_list_notify),","                  text_view)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is important to note that you must use"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"detail strings for the notify signal."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The notify signal is emitted on an object when one of its properties has"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"its value set through "},{"code":"g_object_set_property()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set()"},{"type":"text","text":", et al."}],"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/DBusObjectProxySignalName/notify":{"type":"topic","title":"DBusObjectProxySignalName.notify","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/dbusobjectproxysignalname\/notify","identifier":"do